{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"區塊 (CSS)","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Block/CSS","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>在網頁上一個<strong>區塊</strong>是一個<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a>元素(<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Element\">element</a>)它會出現一個新的行，例：在前面的元素之下和後面的元素之前(通常稱爲塊級元素)。擧個例子, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 標簽就是一個默認的塊級元素，而 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a> 標簽則是一個内聯元素— 你可以在 HTML 源代碼放一些相鄰的鏈接，他們將會并列渲染在相同的行。</p>\n<p>使用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/display\"><code>display</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 屬性你可以隨意改變大多數元素的顯示方式，不論是内聯還是區塊(其中還有很多其他的選項); <strong>blocks</strong> 也同樣會受到定位方案和<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/position\"><code>position</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>屬性的影響。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基礎知識","title":"基礎知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Visual_formatting_model\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">視覺格式模型 (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"在網頁上一個區塊是一個HTML元素(element)它會出現一個新的行，例：在前面的元素之下和後面的元素之前(通常稱爲塊級元素)。擧個例子, <p> (en-US) 標簽就是一個默認的塊級元素，而 <a> 標簽則是一個内聯元素— 你可以在 HTML 源代碼放一些相鄰的鏈接，他們將會并列渲染在相同的行。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Block (CSS)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Block (CSS)","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Block (CSS)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Block (ブロック) (CSS)",